      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont know... sometimes i just sit here and look at my kids coming over to help me with the laundry or the food, and i just feel so heavy. i feel like im just a weight around their necks now. i've spent my whole life taking care of everyone else, but now i'm just... taking. it feels so wrong.",
