    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels like what you're saying... like maybe i'm just making things harder for them by being here. like if i wasn't such a drain on them, they could actually have a real life. do you really think it's better if i just stop trying so hard to stay on top of things?",
